    public abstract class ParameterizableComplexEventPattern
extends ComplexEventPatternImpl
    An extension of the ComplexEventPattern type that additionally captures parameters of the pattern and provides functionality to evaluate parameter bindings at runtime.

    In event processing scenarios where parameter binding is involved, event patterns should extend this superclass.
